strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a027e16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/photo/bkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170125233803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170125233803&h=bd7f06a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n被廉署拘捕另外2名警務人員，其中高級督察陳嘉健為港大尖子，被視為警隊「明日之星」，另一名反黑探員鍾文浩曾是臥底黑幫的「無間道」，去年獲盧偉聰頒發處長嘉許狀。陳和鍾同樣都有反黑經驗及與「O記」有交集。<br />\n<br />\n年僅28歲的陳，被捕前駐守有組織罪案及三合會調查科，他2012年曾接受傳媒訪問，親述投考警隊的經歷，表明身為督察須有熱誠，認為即使面對困難亦不能退縮，且要有承擔去完成每一個任務。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉健2010年畢業於香港大學工程系，大學二年級時參加警隊學長計劃後，立志加入警隊。他後來透過「警務督察招募快線」投考督察，畢業前已通過警隊考核程序，並在畢業後隨即接受警察學院36周的訓練，先擔任軍裝巡邏小隊指揮官，再轉往旺角警區刑事調查隊，曾駐守旺角警區反黑組，其後調任有組織罪案及三合會調查科。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的偵緝警員鍾文浩，2010年11月獲「O記」招攬，滲入黑幫作臥底搜證，協助偵破屯門黑幫「新X安」一宗廝殺案，案中綽號「郭靖」的18歲青年被人用刀襲擊及用汽車輾過死亡，警方其後拘捕疑兇。鍾文浩於2014年6月，以臥底警員身份上庭作供。2016年6月23日，鍾獲警務處處長盧偉聰頒予嘉許狀。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=32e28bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff2cf913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6c125857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e099270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5487b47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8c6ed135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e1fbaed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=15f6a296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1